; Auto-generated placeholder for Babilim, the Iron Crown.
; Drop real environment art under MeshRoot; lighting/atmosphere already tuned.
; Atmosphere: The great city. Eight districts: the High Gate, Market of Tongues, Ziggurat Quarter, Hanging Gardens, Black Sail Docks, Inquisition Square, Old University, Crown Foundry. Vendors, fast-travel anchor, faction halls. Always slightly humming.
; Palette: Lapis · gold · plum-velvet
; Level range: 15-30

