; ── Refugee Spawner. Babilim is the Crown court, so refugees fleeing
; here come predominantly from the Black Sail's reach (smuggler raids
; on Crown shipping) and from the Druid frontier (Inquisition's burn
; chains push Wound-Marked townsfolk inward). Active at SKIRMISH+ on
; the relevant pairs.
[node name="RefugeeSpawner_crown_bs" type="Node3D" parent="."]
script = ExtResource("refugee_spawner_script")
pair_key = &"crown_vs_black_sail"
refugee_count_skirmish = 1
refugee_count_open_war = 2

